data.description:
Discover the allure of Southern living in this enchanting Lowcountry residence nestled in the heart of Beaufort. Boasting the freedom of no HOAs or covenants, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home sits graciously on almost half an acre, offering a haven of comfort and space.Step into the open living floor plan, where the spacious living and dining areas seamlessly merge, creating an inviting atmosphere for both everyday living and entertaining. Natural light dances through the windows, illuminating the warmth of this charming abode.The focal point of this home is the large bonus flex room, a versatile space that beckons you to unwind and entertain. With the added charm of a fireplace, this room becomes the perfect gathering spot for friends and family, creating memories that will last a lifetime.

The well-appointed kitchen invites culinary adventures, featuring modern appliances and ample counter space. The convenience of a washer and dryer that convey adds to the practicality of this home, ensuring that daily tasks are met with ease.

Step outside to a nice-sized fenced yard, a picturesque setting for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying the Lowcountry breeze. The backyard also boasts a shed that conveys with the property, providing additional storage options for all your needs.

Embrace the charm of Beaufort and the freedom to make this house your own. With no HOAs or covenants to limit your creativity, this Lowcountry haven is ready to welcome you home. Seize the opportunity to experience the best of Southern living in this captivating Beaufort residence. Welcome to your new home!
